# Dewey — Project Rules

## What this project is

Dewey is a WordPress admin plugin (requires WP 7.0+, PHP 8.1+) that embeds a floating AI chat assistant into wp-admin. It does two things:

1. **Content Q&A** — RAG pipeline: BM25-style indexed retrieval → AI answer via `wp_ai_client_prompt()` (WordPress Core AI, provider-agnostic through the Connectors plugin).
2. **Admin navigation** — Fuzzy command-palette suggestions using Fuse.js client-side matching against a static command registry and dynamically scraped sidebar items.

The plugin ships no external API keys. All AI calls go through WordPress Core. Dewey does not replace WordPress's own AI tooling — it extends the admin UI with a persistent, context-aware assistant.

